{"tid":1436613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸紅二代軍二代係8月5號微博話中國公安應要求經落馬洲進入香港平暴之後del左post，冇人講？","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:23:33.000Z","uid":254745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb0ed3e9577fe99f8949bcd8730e744f5c9a77a","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"事源係大陸紅二代軍二代 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡小心</span></span><br />\n係2019年8月5號係微博開post話「香港政府向中央求救，公安開始進入平暴」，然後貼落馬洲既定位出黎，之後刪左post，但繼續同啲大陸網民鬥屌，話同佢地賭一億。<br />\n<br />\n蔡小心係好出名既大陸紅二代軍二代，之前七警坐監，話出一萬毆打法官杜大衛（David Dufton）就係佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBoY1eS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBoY1eS.jpg&h=0e47591a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxCrqGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxCrqGy.jpg&h=4a1c53cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq7Cxmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq7Cxmy.jpg&h=46bdabc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果講既係真，問題係佢地唔需要遵守香港法律，打死人都唔怕，追究唔到<br />\n希望唔係真，好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n蔡小心，男，1976年生，抗美援朝战史学者、军史作家。铁原大血战名将蔡长元之子，延安儿女联谊会成员。红西路军后代联谊会发起人之一。<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%94%A1%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=7258f6f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%94%A1%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83</a>"},{"pid":"22a2b8dd934ad68843635d9525ceccae4fab8829","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88b578e1e8321a7b7747807c9f7d5e0bd9a7b2b4","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08e560169b77fbf75b32fef6f52b15ad752c1d55","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d90f2289492267c4d00e88505dd7cc81e3ec0666","tid":1436613,"uid":269512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"逆思考 ： 如果大陸公安非法 ( 暗黑 ) 執法不幸 L 咗，政府會點公佈呢？定係毀 C 滅 J 算呢？"},{"pid":"c96c7090bba879c7a65b0f536bc56eec8f9c931d","tid":1436613,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d85fae4c073d5dc7ee37194ad153803893317c4","tid":1436613,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"紅二代想嚟香港搞獨立？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717d0b2865e3d6dc07fc68f52fd3cfa43646cc1f","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44581405268a7807594bc01e15199448e5c267a5","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7b3c743ebc91adb10b3f6183acbd7e8cc4bde1d","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e45df39f1f4a2d6bfb6781ce3c38aae13bb201d","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cf0481723230546c3b4406cb2f34d254319b1d8","tid":1436613,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eb3c7c893c46e254638bade5c48496cfefa1782","tid":1436613,"uid":160247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQyY76m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQyY76m.jpg&h=31560105&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家記住佢，梁凌杰先生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJfpjfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJfpjfH.jpg&h=11f54868&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n請大家記住佢，盧曉欣同學。<br />\n仲有鄔小姐，麥小姐，仲有其他為香港死既烈士。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都身心俱疲，好重好重既無力感，我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一日抗爭未完，一日仲有人行出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地都仲有希望架<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抖一陣好啦，我地要繼續行出黎，唔好比同路人感到孤單，更加要對得住死去既烈士們。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n今晚同聽日 機場同街頭見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6iqOfx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6iqOfx.png&h=ca29d14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtcWatT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtcWatT.jpg&h=ba8a794d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7JBUVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7JBUVy.jpg&h=656d6305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1B3uvvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1B3uvvp.jpg&h=86caf1af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4116750dfbe2ca6b6f47e3082d753642cf1235bd","tid":1436613,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"由佢9up，問佢幾時去艱苦地區參軍報國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466e70453cddfbcd07f495fc02348a3e7834fdd8","tid":1436613,"uid":264792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep